N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 253.5 - Objections; waiver

State Regulations

An objection not timely urged before the board, director
of PEPR, or designated hearing officer shall be deemed waived unless the
failure to urge such objection shall be excused by the board because of
extraordinary circumstances. Notes
